# Daily Diary - Day 03

## Operators & Control Statements

### Today's Topics
- Arithmetic Operators
- Relational Operators
- Logical Operators
- If-else statements
- Switch case

### Practical Work
- Created calculator using operators
- Implemented grading system with if-else
- Built menu-driven program with switch
- Practiced operator precedence

### Code Example
```java
public class OperatorsDemo {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int a = 10, b = 5;
        
        // Arithmetic
        int sum = a + b;
        boolean isEqual = (a == b);
        
        // Control statements
        if (a > b) {
            System.out.println("a is greater");
        } else {
            System.out.println("b is greater");
        }
    }
}
